title: Elemental Full v1.3.5
description:
***Elemental Full is the version without ads or banners***

If you are a fan of games like Sudoku but you are sick of numbers, Elemental is your game! Use your brain to create elements by mixing earth, air, fire and water to solve puzzles.

Complete puzzles as fast as you can and win the high score. You can use tips that teach you how to mix the elements. Each tip contains a famous quote that you can tweet and share with your friends. If youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re still stuck, you can also place a spell that magically puts a piece on the board right where it belongs!

Sounds easy, right? Not so fast...the more tips and spells you use, the less points you will earn!
You can also connect to OpenFeint and check your scores and ranking against players from all around the world. You can also unlock clever achievements as your skills improve.

Elemental is an app for smartphones and tablets. The game 
is perfect for mobile phones like Samsung Galaxy S2, Samsung Europa, Samsung Galaxy S, Samsung Galaxy Ace, HTC Desire, HTC Evo, Motorola Defy, LG Optimus One and many others.

Elemental is a game with amazing graphics that will challenge your brain and your patience every day!

Available in English, Spanish and Portuguese.

What's in this version:
Music. If the device screen is turned off, the music stops playing
Vibrate. The option of turning off vibration on wrong moves was added to the game
Heyzap. Heyzap integration was removed
Tutorial. If you make a wrong move in the tutorial, youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll have the option of retaking the step instead of start from the beginning again
